		partition LDA = calculated
			mode: import
			source = ```
					
					// This table should contain the last data available in the fact table. This data will be queried by 
					//In the report Id put the value of the reportid from the Power BI Service.
					ROW("report_id", "xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx","LDA", MAX('Dummy Fact Table'[Date]))
					```

